public class Data extends LinkedList<POI>
Data class used for reading and updating JSON files, managing POIs and bookmarks, and generating new POI IDs.

The JSON files are read and POIs are stored in LinkedList objects when Data() is called. POIs and bookmarks are added with the addPOI method and POIs are removed with the removePOI method.

Example Use: 
 
     new Data();
     addPOI(p, userCreatedPOIs);
     removePOI(p2, bookmarks);
Example Output: No output, but userCreatedPOIs, and bookmarks list are updated accordingly along with the associated JSON files.
